{
  "prompt": "Amar naam Ramesh. Ami Karnataka-e ekjon thika sromik. Ami mashe prai 5563 taka rojgar kori. Amar kono likhito chukti nei. Ami kon kon sorkari kollan prokolper jonno joggo? Prokolpogulir naam bolun.",
